ALDRICH, Nickalous N., 21, Lance Cpl., Marines; Austin, Tex.; First Marine Division.

ANDERSON, Carl L. Jr., 21, Airman First Class, Air Force; Georgetown, S.C.; Third Logistics Readiness Squadron.

HOLLEYMAN, Aaron N., 26, Staff Sgt., Army; Glasgow, Mont.; First Battalion, Fifth Special Forces Group.

LOPEZ, Edgar E., 27, Sgt., Marines; Los Angeles; 24th Marine Expeditionary Unit, Second Expeditionary Force.

SKINNER, Nicholas M., 20, Pfc., Marines; Davenport, Iowa; 11th Marine Expeditionary Unit, First Expeditionary Force.